Description:
Style & Elegance In The Heart Of Casey
A residence like no other, this impressively spacious home caters for the largest of families and is situated in one of the best estates in Cranbourne East.
Flawlessly appointed from top to bottom you will appreciate the grand entry foyer, elegant formal lounge that leads with ease to an amazing kitchen that features stone benchtops, glass splashback, quality Blanco stainless appliances & a huge amount of storage.
The adjoining casual family & meals area offer a relaxed space plus it features a separate rumpus room, home theater to the rear of the home. Cleverly designed with 6 generously proportioned bedrooms (2 with ensuites), 3 bathrooms it offers accommodation that's rarely found.
Extras include: ducted heating, ducted cooling & ducted vacuum, alarm system, spa bath and list goes on.
Outdoors features include beautifully landscaped rear courtyard and an under-cover entertaining area that provides a fine balance to the spacious interiors.
For those looking to make a statement this is the one. Homes of this quality rarely come to the marketplace. Act quickly to avoid disappointment.
Insights: 19 Armstrong Street, Cranbourne East VIC 3977 was last sold in 2017.

Description:
EXCEPTIONAL ENTERTAINER!
If you have been looking for your dream home, a place where you can simply move in, unpack and relax then an inspection is a must! this 36.88sq home(approx.) is ideally suited to those requiring multiple living zones this fine example of family living is within close proximity to picturesque parkland and public transportation!
The master comes complete with a full ensuite including duel vanities, extended shower space and separate toilet facility, as well as walk in robes and built in robes for additional storage. The remaining three bedrooms are all finished with built in robes with the fourth having a walk in robe of its own.
If you enjoy entertaining family and guests of all sizes then be taken back my the numerous living areas on offer, whether you?re enjoying a new release in the theatre, reading a good book in the formal lounge or simply enjoying some down time with the kids in the children?s retreat/huge open study, this home is sure to accommodate even the largest of families.
The hostess kitchen is a chef's dream and is complete with quality stainless steel appliances including a dish washer, 900mm range hood, 5 burner gas cook top, tiled splash back, ample amounts of bench and overhead storage space, not to mention a butler?s pantry. All of this overlooking the separate dining area and outdoor entertaining zone.
Added features include: Quality hardwood floors, down lights, internal access, ducted heating & split system cooling, plantation shutters throughout, fully landscaped front and rear yard, large scale garden shed, high ceilings and neutral tones throughout.
Step outside to your landscaped rear yard complete with your alfresco and feature wall. This will provide the perfect spot to sit back and unwind after the long working week or to even start up the family BBQ.
This is a tremendous opportunity for a family who insists on nothing but the best! Surrounded by top end properties and is within walking distance to picturesque wetlands, this home boasts convenience. Other estate features include Class-A recycled water ensuring lush gardens year round, over 14 hectares of parkland and public open space, public BBQ facilities, playgrounds and walking tracks.
Those who are business savvy will appreciate this Telstra smart community positioned within a short drive to all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne.
Minutes away from freeway access enroute to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, the recently constructed Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre and the Town Centre. Not to mention just seconds away from the newly developed Selanda rise and hunt Club village shopping centres.
BOOK AN INSPECTION TODAY, IT MAY BE GONE TOMORROW! - *PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS*

Description:
**UNDER OFFER / UNDER CONTRACT**
CASCADES ON CLYDE, CRANBOURNE EAST (123975058): Young, fresh and with plenty of space for any growing family, this home is located in the ever popular Cascades On Clyde estate and is impressive enough to beg the question ? why bother building?
Ready to move in and enjoy with external features including a stylish rendered facade and a landscaped front garden, inside you will find plenty of living space and accommodation to delight all who inspect.
The tiled hallway is flanked by a formal lounge, large kitchen with stone benchtops and stainless steel appliances plus a vast family/meals area. There?s also a separate rumpus room that would be perfect as a kid's play retreat or for the home theatre you have always wanted!
There are 3 oversized robed bedrooms, including the master with a walk in wardrobe and a stylish ensuite that is complemented by an equally impressive family bathroom and second toilet. A host of additional extras add to its appeal such as ducted heating and evaporative cooling, an alarm system plus a double garage with remote door and secure internal access.
The huge backyard, overall land size of app. 594m2, offers enough open space for the kids and pets to run amuck, whilst the large decked pergola is sure to impress given its sheer size and entertaining capabilities.
This is a tremendous opportunity for those who insist on nothing but the best! Surrounded by top end properties the location is very appealing and is within close proximity to picturesque wetlands. Other estate features include Class-A recycled water, ensuring lush gardens year round, over 14 hectares of public open space, BBQ facilities and walking tracks.
Those who are business savvy will appreciate this Telstra smart community positioned within a short drive to all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne. Minutes away from freeway access enroute to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre and the Selandra Rise shopping centre only a brisk drive away!

Description:
Investors Take Note!
This lovely, three bedroom family home is a property not to be missed as it is located close to Cranbourne East secondary college, Cranbourne Park shopping complex, Casey Race sports centre, public transport and parks.
Upon entry you are greeted with light the filled lounge room that has a gas fire place to set the warm and inviting ambience, this then leads you to the tiled kitchen that is fully equipped with a gas burner cooktop, a dishwasher and plenty of cupboard and bench space for the chef of the family to prepare a delicious meal that can be enjoyed in the family meals area.
Comprising of three bedrooms; the master positioned at the front of the home with a walk in robe and its very own en-suite. The remaining two bedrooms have built in robes and are nearby to the central bathroom with a bath. Further comforts include a gas wall furnace and a wall mounted air conditioner.
As you make your way outside you will find the well maintained yard which wraps around the roofed patio as well as a double garage to secure your cars in.
This fantastic home is currently tenanted until the 05/06/2017 with outstanding tenants and a rental amount of $1,564 a month. Perfect for those looking to invest, so make your enquiry today and snatch up a great opportunity.

Description:
OUTSTANDING FAMILY HOME LOCATED IN PRESTIGIOUS POCKET!!!
CRANBOURNE EAST: Located in the highly sort after Cascades on Clyde Estate, Ideally suited to those requiring multiple living zones this home is a fine example of family living at its best and is within close proximity to an abundance of local amenities.
The open floor plan itself offers three spacious bedrooms, the generous sized master comes complete with walk in robe and a full en suite. In addition the surrounding guest bedrooms are all fitted out with walk in robes of their own.
The kitchen comes complete with quality stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, 600mm range hood, 4-burner gas cook top, ample overhead cupboard/storage space and tiled splash back all this and a whole lot more overlooking the separate meals zone.
Take a load off and relax in your theatre room or huge rear living zone, this space offers exceptional potential to entertain even the largest of friends and family.
Added features include: ducted heating, split system cooling, internal access, down lights throughout, plantation shutters, rear roller door, exposed aggregate driveway, fully landscaped front and rear yard and neutral tones throughout.
Step outside and enjoy your quality built, large scale pitched roof pergola. There is a convenient mix of grass and pavement providing enough room for children and adults to enjoy their own unique space.
Surrounded by picturesque wetlands and walk ways, estate features also include Class-A recycled water ensuring lush gardens year round, over 14 hectares of parkland and public open space, public BBQ facilities and playgrounds. Those who are business savvy will also appreciate the estates Telstra Velocity smart wiring.
Minutes away from Freeway access en route to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre, not to mention walking distance from the Selandra rise shopping centre and hunt club village!

STUNNING FEATURE PACKED FAMILY HOME
In the highly sought after Cascades on Clyde Estate is this superb near new home with upgrades a plenty! Accommodation comprises 4 good sized bedrooms, full ensuite & walk in robe to master, 3 generous living areas and a fully appointed kitchen (island bench & SS appliances) overlooking the living & dining. The near new presentation is flawless both inside and out with quality fittings & fixtures, widened hallways & raised ceilings! Added extras include ducted heating, evaporative cooling, internal access from the remote double garage (which also has a rear roller door for access) plus alfresco. All this set on an incredible 595m2 of land there's still plenty of room for the kids and pets.

Description:
LOCATION, SIZE & FEATURES UNDER THE ONE ROOF.
This very uniquely designed HUNT CLUB property sits on a massive 787sqm (approx.) allotment. And is a stone's throw away from the Cranbourne East Primary School, Cranbourne East Secondary College, child care centre, public transport and the brand new Hunt Club Village Shopping Centre.
The interior is modern, elegant and relaxing. When you step onto the property, you are welcomed by its beautifully landscaped gardens & massive driveway that leads to the side access. Upon entrance of this home there is a large formal living area/theatre room with a timber feature wall. The floor plan then flows onto a large family dining & family living area as well as an enormous rumpus room like nothing you would've ever seen. The Rumpus room has enough space for a large seating area as well as space for table tennis table or a pool table, and to top that off, you have the installed bar, feature fireplace and timber feature ceilings in the middle of this enormous room as well as bi-fold doors that open all the way to give you a view of the large landscaped backyard that this home offers. All of this is centered by a fantastic kitchen that offers plenty of cupboard and bench space as well glass splash back & stainless steel appliances.
The sleeping quarters of this property consist of 4 large bedrooms, master with full enuiste & WIR as well as BIRs for 2 of the other bedrooms.
This home also features a large outdoor salon allowing you to run a business from home or you can even use this salon as a studio with 2 additional bedrooms and toilet or even a man cave if you choose to, the choice is yours.
The number of features on the outside of this property are also sure to impress, with side access and an allocated section in the backyard to park, cars, caravans, trailer or even boats. Landscaped gardens back & front as well as private walkway on the side that goes straight through to the salon.
- 4 large bedrooms.
- 3 Huge separate Large living areas
- Kitchen with glass splash back & stainless steel appliances.
- Quality light fittings throughout, feature timber walls & celing & feature fireplace.
- Ducted heating & air condition.
- External Salon/studio with 3 separate rooms and a basin & toilet.
- Solar hot water, CCTV, garden shed, BI-fold doors, tinted windows, Bar, water feature & much more
- Side access and parking space for caravans, trailers etc.
